text: Javier Raxón (born 3 December 1944) is a Guatemalan wrestler. He competed in two events at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Guatemalan male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Guatemala Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
